Features to add (current as of 09/03/2013):
===========================================
(a) Should span DOM elements correctly.
(b) Should highlight only if triggered on.
(c) Choose the color of the highlight.
(d) Save and load the highlighted page (to help print the page with the highlights).
(e) Allow annotations. User clicks at a spot where she would like to annotate. A text box pops up and is saved with the annotated document.
